
                        VarArray version 1.0

The VarArray library provides easy-to-handle variable size multi-dimensional arrays
for the C/C++ programmer.


Installation Instructions
=========================

To create the library, type:

   1)  ./configure <config parameters like --prefix= ... see INSTALL>
   2)  make 

To compile and run the optional test programs:

   make check

To install the var_array library and the var_array include files:

   make install


VarArray Documentation
======================

For documentation on the VarArray library, please see the file
   ./doc/multi-dim-arrays.html


